Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京租界確認到巨大的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據推測是報告中提到的Freyja彈頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍滯留在神根島是否妥當?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨 一切都交給修奈澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般市民當場死亡人數逾千萬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後受害者推測將達到2500萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為醫療設施也被完全破壞 無法對市民進行及時救治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京租界已死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是…我…幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這已經不是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再次使用這種兵器 黑騎士團將全軍覆滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 眼下…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍降落至東京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 朝比奈遇難 除此之外還有眾多犧牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管這些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最優先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍動員搜尋娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個ZERO已經…

Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛


Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡者逃往左側跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 請先重編軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇

Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草


Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉婭?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為逃走的是維蕾塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 毫無節操的電視製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO幹的嗎 皇女殿下成了俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何不再給我多一點信任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準腿部 活捉她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是布里塔尼亞的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 我們是布里塔尼亞的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無戰鬥意願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交特使?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水無瀨 那台機體是通過正式管道申請的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 親自深入敵人腹地?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂 叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親自去指揮搜救部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 傑雷米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉一定還活著 找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後退至幕張後 重整戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍緊急撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂 我叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要哥哥沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時休戰是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼俾斯麥要撤兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因正在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎沒有交戰意向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 東京也暫時停戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO的指示嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在哥哥身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不也就我們兩人堅持至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想讓哥哥靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事等一下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 雖然也許沒太大意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥這裡有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會有它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是原本打算給娜娜莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想代替娜娜莉 冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒察覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我痛恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深惡痛絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾次想害死你 不過未能如願而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去 別再出現在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 我仍舊沒意識到 會造成怎樣的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 你必須做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拋棄科學保留人心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是捨棄人心來投身科學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊德老師也遇到過這種選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就道德敗壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點自知之明還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我製造的Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 ZERO不接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有ZERO也得與修奈澤爾進行會談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們的頭頭是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先斬後奏是不是有點不妥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠殺 婦女兒童一個不放過 是ZERO指使的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈爾特 為什麼沒有馬上抓住修奈澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一架Knightmare護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這機會為朝比奈報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的專機上裝載有Freyja彈頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Freyja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引發剛才巨大爆炸的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡爆炸的話 我們和ZERO都難以倖免
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知修奈澤爾打的什麼算盤 但現在只能由我們去會會他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去檢修回歸的紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那交涉由我、千葉、迪特哈爾特 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 找不到扇那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉殿下 您一定要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是我在教團中的所見所聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 科奈莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 忙著照顧你們打傷的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城 剛才我也說過請自覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑騎士團內務清潔副官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做為事務總長扇要的代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的一廂情願
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請務必到場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞是ZERO最元老級的志同道合者 身經百戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 我曾被你所救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來道一聲謝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我和你之間的關係還真是奇妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運終究讓我們成為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去找娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存者排隊登錄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名年齡住所血型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要救治的人去醫務接待台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為避免混亂 請保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 你活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次和ZERO未分勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須先確認會談內容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想他也不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他並不是樂於與人討論的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自背負一切 與他人疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這口吻貌似很熟悉ZERO的為人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你更瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是我和科奈莉婭的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖布里塔尼亞帝國前第11皇子 魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最深愛卻又敬畏的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是布里塔尼亞的皇子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈爾特 你不可能毫無察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該從傑雷米亞和維蕾塔那裡獲得過情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費心機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠這種言論令我們自亂陣腳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認可ZERO是因為他引發的奇跡而並非家譜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些奇跡如果有弄虛作假的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄虛作假?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO有特殊能力 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強制對方服從命令的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把它理解成一種強效的催眠術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這力量是奇跡之神?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說我們家ZERO的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他天資聰穎膽識過人 可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼皇子和GEASS 有證據嗎 證據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據在此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真身是布里塔尼亞前皇子魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GEASS的力量操縱人心的 騙子



Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO一直把我們蒙在鼓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 把我們作為棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢 扇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這如果當真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 不能否認ZERO至今為止的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果真有GEASS的話 不是很令人鼓舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將成為對抗布里塔尼亞的強有力武器

Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這份力量只對敵人使用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道對我們也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他操縱自己的親妹妹尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠殺了前來參加日本特區的11區人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是正義的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要證據的話就在這


Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 你對尤菲使用了GEASS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她屠殺日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次屠殺是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而非我的妹妹

Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO下令屠殺日本人…

Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是偽造的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是 被懷疑使用過GEASS的事件與人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁 片瀨少將也…

Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛維斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也深受其害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來高亥的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞投降過來 全都得以說明

Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也無法保證自己有沒有被他的GEASS操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想的話 著實可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們也…

Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們曾將Freyja彈頭的事告知過ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為避免無謂的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot上留有通信紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 沒有告訴我們


Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO無法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼的相信他….

Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們對他來說…只是棋子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生 ZERO這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位能否交出我的弟弟ZERO


Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇?

Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有討價還價的餘地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願聞其詳

Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日本還來

Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛自己曾經相信的夥伴

Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要換回日本 不然我無法原諒自己

Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 請脫下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手構不著的話 我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 無法觸及之處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 能進來嗎 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮


Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇希望你去四號倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四號?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體情況我也不清楚


Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請脫下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試看


Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被抓住的時候 你們都做了些甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 這個C.C. …

Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了記憶

Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的錯

Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你認識的C.C. 已經不在了

Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 不在 娜娜莉也走了

Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那魯魯修呢

Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 你沒事就好

Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉營救來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 我和娜娜莉談了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她幫了我

Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候說也許不合適 我的哥哥…

Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧 ZERO

Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟將我們玩弄於鼓掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經知道你的GEASS

Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說的英雄ZERO 壯志未成身先死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他勇敢的生前事蹟 將被人們永久傳頌

Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈爾特 這就是你的劇本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算拍完你戰勝布里塔尼亞的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 節目被腰斬了

Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 雖然Knightmare礙事 但扇他們毫無防備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷使用GEASS的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都那麼相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井上和吉田也是為你而死

Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這樣太單方面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧ZERO我們才走到今天不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聽他一言

Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 卡蓮

Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和ZERO陪葬嗎


Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會中了GEASS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說 我是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意和你…


Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你幹的…


Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那看來沒機會了…

Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 事到如今才察覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不過是棋子而已


Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO

Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修

Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮


Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一顆特別優秀的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這不過是一盤棋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎


Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉鎗


Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 你要活下去

Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開鎗

Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 連蜃氣樓一起解決

Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥由我保護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 羅洛

Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了 蜃氣樓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巴別塔那時一樣

Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞 ZERO逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mordred能抓住嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對守護領域的計算沒想到這麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 我已經沒有活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這動作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓你死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大範圍使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 這樣下去你的心臟承受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全員 蜃氣樓被偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有戰鬥單位全力摧毀蜃氣樓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 摧毀蜃氣樓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被人作為道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…住手 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是教團的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…救我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後又被哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確也許只是被哥哥利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那段時光是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為那段回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於可以 成為人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 別使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的意志

Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 為什麼救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是謊話吧 說什麼想殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞不過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的弟弟

Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對哥哥…最瞭解…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥是個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴大搜索範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請增派地面班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉 羅洛 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是結局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 報應才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因為如此 謝謝 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救回的這條性命 對我來說還有必須做完的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 會被迫使用這裡的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸神的黃昏的接續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊的世界會被毀滅 新的世界將會被創造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾父 查爾斯．D．布里塔尼亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去地獄的路上 少不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…

Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我和你到底是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經知曉了真相  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,追隨我到最後的 竟然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我總是後知後覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是魯路修·Vi·布里塔尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而是魯路修·蘭佩路基的弟弟
